snippet.title: [Lets Review] Old Warriors OC: Amberstar
snippet.description:
So I'd set this up to have a little character talking for me, but I couldn't decide on one to stick with so it's just kind of blank. I know the formatting seems odd and some points sound weird (and so do I bc I can't talk unscripted to save my kercheeny), but I unnecessarily put twelve whole hours just about into editing this and I'll be bamboozled if I don't take some pride in it. 

O boi. So yeah I figured I'd do something artsy to revive this ded channel. Lotsa  coughs n sniffles. 

DeviantART: http://espeonumbreonlover.deviantart.com/

Link to speedpaint in the back: (to be uploaded)
__________________________________________
Buncha legal stuff so oof:
Warriors belongs to the Erin Hunter team.
Character and art belong to me. (other than that casual intruding Graystripe... nosy little hoe)
The music is definitally not mine. I used like three different sources and I lost like two of the links so plz dont sue me 
a href="http://www.hooksounds.com" - Music by HookSounds
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UFbTmZfEvgw
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rIVG1TGpMsE
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F4JyuNLiVmQ

I take no claim to the music whatsoever and I tried to get all copyright free. 
Audio Library is one source
Mitch Music is another.
